-- | be A(\_tmp1\_, \_tmp2\_). 1. Let \_tmp4\_ be F(). 1. Let \_tmp5\_ be
-- | E(\_tmp4\_). 1. Let \_tmp6\_ be \_tmp3\_ + \_tmp5\_. 1. Return \_tmp6\_.
-- |
-- | where the various \_tmpN\_ aliases are ephemeral and visible only in
-- | these steps.
