-- SPEC: L24739-L24745
-- | # ThisBooleanValue ( \_value\_: an ECMAScript language value, ): either a normal completion containing a Boolean or a throw completion
-- |
-- | 1\. If \_value\_ is a Boolean, return \_value\_. 1. If \_value\_ is an
