-- SPEC: L25283-L25299
-- | # The AggregateError Constructor
-- |
-- | The AggregateError constructor:
-- |
-- | - is [%AggregateError%]{.dfn}.
-- | - is the initial value of the \*\"AggregateError\"\* property of the
