-- | 𝔽(ℝ(\_prim\_)). 1. Else, let \_n\_ be \_prim\_. 1. Else, 1. Let \_n\_ be
-- | \*+0\*~𝔽~. 1. If NewTarget is \*undefined\*, return \_n\_. 1. Let \_O\_
-- | be ? OrdinaryCreateFromConstructor(NewTarget,
